{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act37side", "eventName": "追跡日落以西", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GO-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "廢鐵與鉚釘", "storyInfo": "維娜為了解決城裡各種矛盾而焦頭爛額，好在格拉斯哥幫依舊陪在她的身邊給予她力所能及的協助。希勒少尉因傷病而痛苦，戴菲恩及時出現，承諾帶他回到麗茵卡登。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g5_noblehall", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海蒂小姐，我還是很難想像。我們好不容易回到了這座偉大的城市，你卻又要離開。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，也許你是該回到你父親的身邊了。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回多倫郡嗎？……嗯，也許吧。不過說不定我會走得更遠一點。畢竟我生命中引領我的人可不只有我父親一個啊。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，您的建議也總是能給我啟發。像是您剛才提到那次與馬奇伯爵的使者共進晚宴的經歷，就讓我學到了不少。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，您這位遠離政治、專心寫小說的作家，想要創作一些歷史故事，我當然很樂意提供第一手資料。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有您剛才說的，把我最熟悉的故鄉多倫郡和倫蒂尼姆這場驚心動魄的戰爭一起寫進故事裡。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。要坦然回顧那些不太光彩的歲月確實不容易，但我們在這座城市裡所做的一切總該有人記得。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英雄……您說得對，或許我們都算是英雄。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#9$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，這樣的愛情故事一定很迷人。一名遠在維多利亞邊境的少女和來倫蒂尼姆度假的青年一見鍾情。可惜青年最終戰死在倫蒂尼姆的戰場上。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，最後少女發現消息是假的。她的愛人沒有死，而是作為英雄回到了她的身邊。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這想法很好，海蒂小姐，失而復得的愛人，就像這座城市——曾被外人踐踏，最終卻由我們親手拯救。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他們開始奏樂了。聽啊，雖然宴會上沒有紅酒與甜點，燈火也不如從前那樣明亮，但銅管樂聲依舊清澈，不曾沙啞。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您移步舞池吧，把您的靈感，還有我，都留在這窗台邊就好。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#11$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那請問您的這兩位朋友——", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位來自異鄉的使者恐怕還不太熟悉維多利亞的禮儀，您就放他一馬吧？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，當然。", "name": "誇誇其談的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……海蒂小姐。這是您的名字，是嗎？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊。我可以帶你們四處走走。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不用了，不麻煩您了。剛才多謝您替我們解圍。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實這裡從來不拒絕任何客人。如果兩位有興趣，下次可以從客廳的大門走進來，而不是窗台。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您的好意。但……其實我對貴族們的宴會沒那麼感興趣。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的貴族政治，是我最早調查的內容之一。我很清楚你們的禮儀、對感染者的態度，甚至連你們的舞步……我也學過。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不說我這個三流小說家有沒有資格自稱貴族……您問過身邊這位士兵，她為什麼帶您來這裡嗎？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——不，不是她帶我來的，是我自作主張！", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，海蒂小姐，對不起。他說想留在倫蒂尼姆更深入瞭解我們的感染者問題，所以我才帶他四處看看……偶爾用點不太光明正大的方法。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您想取笑他，就直接笑吧。他這個人就是這樣，不會說謊，也藏不住心事。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，很像他的身分……“赤心”。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧先生，您是赤心醫療的代表，對吧？", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得我們機構有這麼大的名氣……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對感染者問題有興趣的人，其實很好認。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，要識破貴族們那些心照不宣的謊言恐怕就沒那麼容易了。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——比如說，現在手挽著手走進舞池的那些人，裡面有一半以上都是感染者。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理論上，這是可以預期的。薩卡茲散播的源石粉塵影響了所有倫蒂尼姆市民，不分貴賤、不論地位，可是……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人會說破的。沒有人會去探究，站在自己身邊的人是不是感染者。這是他們為自己保留的體面，也是一種……幻想。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧望向大廳。牆柱上殘留著金飾被剝去後留下的坑坑洞洞，訴說著這裡曾被戰爭踐踏。可樂手們全心投入的演奏幾乎掩蓋了眼前的荒涼與殘破。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自稱小說家的女士扭開鋼筆筆帽，在筆記本上潦草地寫下了什麼。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，您也可以認為在連溫飽都是問題的時候，這些不過是毫無意義的自我安慰。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，我不會這麼想。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這只是一種生活與另一種生活。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這是？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛隨手記下的東西，一個不值一讀的故事大綱……還有一點額外的資訊，請收下。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#10$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一種預感，埃利西奧先生，我們還會再見面。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#11$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，請容許我多問一句——您似乎有什麼痛苦，而且是這些幻想無法撫平的。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#5$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我只是偶爾會想念一位朋友。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#2$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她離開之後，能與我說真話的人又少了一個。", "name": "海蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_400_1#7$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g8_siegeoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“萬國峰會”……？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭方面對維多利亞的局勢非常關注，畢竟這場災難的源頭來自薩卡茲。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您和議會目前在處理流竄薩卡茲問題時的果斷態度，確實讓我看到了這座城市復甦的希望。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，教宗閣下的本意也是希望能為泰拉各國搭建和平對話的橋梁，避免這種生靈塗炭的慘劇再度發生。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不過，你今天來恐怕不只是單純代表拉特蘭教宗閣下來徵求我的答覆吧？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是名信使，我的職責是把消息原封不動地傳遞給您和議會。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，那麻煩替我向教宗閣下表達歉意。我明白拉特蘭的善意，但現在議會顧不上倫蒂尼姆之外的事情。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，請把我的話帶給那位招待你的大公爵——我不會以任何身分前往拉特蘭。至於他自己的計劃，什麼時候輪得到議會或輪得到我來過問呢？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這正是信使的職責。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫·亞吉奧拉斯——根據情報，戰爭期間他曾待在高多汀公爵的高速軍艦上，但並未以拉特蘭的名義直接參戰。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和我猜的差不多。高多汀本人是不是也喜歡吃甜食？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果真是這樣，現在的倫蒂尼姆恐怕沒多少好東西能招待他。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……難得今天是議會的休息日。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……有個比較有趣的小道消息。當時那位拉特蘭信使帶了一隊難民上艦，為了說服公爵接納他們，他甚至把手放在銃械上發誓。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後呢？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後他的手被過熱的銃管燙出了一個水泡。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。怎麼突然講這個？很重要嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休息日。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，算是讓我稍微放鬆一下了。接下來我該先處理哪邊的消息？法陣殘跡的調查？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜的目光落在“希勒少尉”的名字上。又一封信。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她嘆了口氣，把信件放進了待辦事項的籃子裡。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩，這裡有——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-100,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，維娜！你說的那群搶劫的混蛋，我們已經逮到他們還好好教訓了一頓！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "專挑那些體弱的礦石病中晚期患者下手，實在令人不齒。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更噁心的是，還有不少欺善怕惡的傢伙被他們的名號吸引想要加入。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好你消息靈通，沒讓他們壯大起來。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我也想出去活動一下。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-100,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_396_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，連你的份一起揍了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有收上來的謝禮也幫你留了一份。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這又不是什麼收保護費的事——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "55_i06_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 85.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到維多利亞後，你有多久沒吃糖了？", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因陀羅……", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個被搶的小子說是他自己做的，每根都是不同的奇怪口味。剛好你也不喜歡普通的甜味棒棒糖，對吧？", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說為了代替他無法弄到手的標準糖精，他試了馬鈴薯、紅蘿蔔，甚至是地下通道的源石蟲體液……", "name": "達格達"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我全都試過，沒問題的！", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來還滿提神的，我能試一下嗎？", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，想要多少都有！", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……維娜，你還好吧？", "name": "達格達"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，現在吃到什麼都習慣了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……議長的事務呢？", "name": "達格達"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，你現在是在操心什麼？法令草案？公文？還是什麼報告信？", "name": "摩根"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有沒有什麼需要我們幫忙的？特別是那種你自己不方便出手揍人的！", "name": "摩根"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次我還收了個跟班呢！那傢伙瘦得跟竹竿一樣，不過我應該能教他點自衛的拳術。", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格拉斯哥幫也該重新壯大起來了，維娜，我們什麼時候可以回——", "name": "因陀羅"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "達格達"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "摩根"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因陀羅撓了撓頭。就算同伴不用埋怨的眼神看著她，她自己也反應過來了。她不該問的。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜的目光掃過桌上堆積如山的文件。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩走到她身邊，若無其事地從她手裡抽走幾張信紙。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想差不多該公開回應市民關心的問題了。雖然大多數人不會來旁聽議會的討論，但至少他們在一天辛勞結束後還能從收音機裡聽到消息。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在城內的狀況逐漸穩定，我已經向議會申請派遣第三批工程隊進駐諾伯特區。很快，我們的家就能恢復原樣了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是比以前更好！", "name": "摩根"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩，等這些事處理完，很快你就能回麗茵卡登了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g7_towngreenhouse", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？黛安——", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……長官？！", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經退役了……莎拉女士。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，好吧，長官。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你之前拒絕了療養院的邀請，這次是……", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，只是來看看你們，也順便再向你道謝……請不要介意。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我已經記不太清楚了。您也知道，醫生說那些石頭已經蔓延到我腦袋裡了——您的手在發抖。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必在我面前隱藏，長官，您教過我很多知識。幸好這些我都還記得。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來像是某種藥物成癮的症狀。是戰爭時留下的後遺症？", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……止痛劑用多了。就那次在城牆下摔傷留下的毛病。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您必須留下。我去找療養院的醫生，他們說不定有辦法……", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者至少，至少能盡可能幫您找到——", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更多的止痛劑？呵，的確能減輕一些痛苦。", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#5$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您來這裡就是為了這個吧？雖然城裡的物資緊缺，但或許院長會願意想辦法為您拿一些出來。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟戴菲恩閣下一直很照顧療養院，也關心我們。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請稍等我一下，我馬上回來。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#2$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想要留下，這樣他或許真的能夠拿到些已經不夠再配發給他的止痛劑。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1520_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——", "name": "希勒少尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1520_1#2$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 2.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸……人呢？", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g6_dusklentiavenue", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 3.5, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，走路不看路啊！", "name": "路人的聲音"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離他遠一點，沒看到他不太對勁嗎？", "name": "路人的聲音"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議長辦公室，應該在……這邊……嘶……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他倒下了！又是一個礦石病晚期的倒楣鬼嗎？", "name": "路人的聲音"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別靠近！要是他崩解了，我們全都完蛋……", "name": "路人的聲音"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我……不是……嘖，快要控制不了身體了。", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去找人來！大家快讓開，讓開！", "name": "路人的聲音"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g15_eveningglow_L1", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希勒少尉倒在街道上，夕陽的光線不算刺眼，卻依舊讓他的眼睛泛起酸澀……"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者說，他的身體又在提醒他——痛苦，必須用另一種生理性的渴望來填補。"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他試著調整呼吸，就像過去他親手輔導那些在戰場上被折磨至極的士兵一樣……"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他失敗了，他早已被痛苦擊潰。"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希勒看到了火，灼熱的火焰讓他難以睜開雙眼。天邊的火、城牆上的火、在他身上燃燒的火——"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "55_i07_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他彷彿又回到了那一天，倒在城牆下的那一刻。"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆那雄偉的城牆，在德拉克的火焰中熊熊燃燒，火光越來越旺，越來越炙熱，直到吞沒整片天空。"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他害怕地嘶吼，試圖遮住自己的雙眼——"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "cg", "id": "55_i07_2", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……少尉……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希勒……少尉……快……起來……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 3.5, "type": "cg", "id": "55_i07_2", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看到了一隻手伸向了自己。"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "55_i07_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴……戴菲恩小姐？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直在等你來找我，少尉。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了你寄給維娜的信……但你故意避開了我，就像你拒絕了我為你提供的治療一樣。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她最後也沒有看那封信……對吧，戴菲恩小姐？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我大概能猜到你在信裡寫了什麼。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，但這次，我幫不了你。我們都很清楚倫蒂尼姆的藥物供應狀況……你不能留在這裡。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那我，還能去哪？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茵卡登。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——不！我……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是請求，是命令，少尉。也別拿你已經退役的身分來搪塞我。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你在猶豫什麼，也知道你害怕什麼。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你害怕面對“加拉瓦鐵盾”那些背叛你、拋棄你的長官們……", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "害怕自己不能履行對我，還有對我母親的承諾……更害怕帶著這副模樣回到家鄉，不是嗎？", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……不知道……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少尉，你沒有自己想的那麼堅強，而我，也沒有你以為的那麼脆弱與高貴。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都是麗茵卡登人……這裡，本來就不是我們的家。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少尉，戰爭已經結束了。士兵該回家了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用怕，少尉，我會陪你一起回家。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g15_eveningglow_L2", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 479, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嗚咽）可是我現在這副樣子……真的還能撐到回家嗎……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會安排好的。而且你不會真以為只要避著我，我就會放任你不管吧？", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝您，戴菲恩小姐……", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您……還會回倫蒂尼姆嗎？", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會，這也是我對維娜的承諾。不過她可能還要再等我一陣子。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先安置你在城內療養，等我處理完手邊的事，我們就出發吧。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 488, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……遵命，戴菲恩小姐。", "name": "希勒少尉"}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茵卡登……媽媽，我也要回家了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}}, {"id": 490, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 491, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 492, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 493, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 494, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 495, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 496, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}